Stockton.Taft Mosswood, California:
Taft Mosswood is a census-designated place (CDP) in San Joaquin County, California, United States. The population was 1,530 at the 2010 census, up from 1,388 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
Taft Mosswood is located at 37°54′59″N 121°16′54″W (37.916324, -121.281563).
